<section class="nolo-pitch-section">
  <div class="pitch-container">
    <div class="line-container">
      <div class="vertical-line"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="pitch-intro nolo-reveal">
      <p>For the empowered Product Operations leader, this is your opportunity to transform how your brand launches products. Our battle-tested components and proven implementation approach mean you can deliver real results that fit around your existing systems.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pitch-card nolo-reveal">
      <h2>Lead Product Operations Forward</h2>
      <p>Your product teams are creating amazing things, but operations haven't kept pace. While development and creative push boundaries, launches are still orchestrated through spreadsheets and status meetings. You see the opportunity: streamlined product operations could unlock your brand's true potential. It's operations leaders like you who drive real transformation.</p>
      
      <div class="pill-box-container">
        <div class="pill-box nolo-reveal">
          <div class="connecting-line"></div>
          <div class="pills-wrapper">
            <div class="nolo-pill" style="--delay: 0s;">Rigid Systems</div>
            <div class="nolo-pill" style="--delay: 0.2s;">Data Silos</div>
            <div class="nolo-pill" style="--delay: 0.4s;">Roadmapped</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pitch-outro nolo-reveal">
      <p>Transform your product operations with the Nolo Framework: A proven system that grows with your brand. Start with core workflows, then expand strategically. Built on Airtable, backed by battle-tested components, delivered by experts who understand how product-driven brands innovate.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="author-badge nolo-reveal">
      <div class="author-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 200 100" class="nolo-svg-logo">
          <!-- Approximating Nolo dash logo for icon -->
          <g fill="#1a1a1a">
            <rect x="20" y="20" width="30" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            <rect x="60" y="20" width="30" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            <rect x="100" y="20" width="30" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            <rect x="140" y="20" width="30" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            
            <rect x="20" y="45" width="20" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            <rect x="50" y="45" width="40" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            <rect x="100" y="45" width="20" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            
            <rect x="20" y="70" width="30" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            <rect x="60" y="70" width="30" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
            <rect x="100" y="70" width="30" height="15" rx="7.5"/>
          </g>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="author-details">
        <strong>Oliver Rhodes</strong>
        <span>Co-Founder, Nolo Apps</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

